us: Zwei Coronavirusf\u00e4lle in T\u00fcbingen|last=Germany|first=Stuttgarter Zeitung, Stuttgart|website=stuttgarter-zeitung.de|language=de|access-date=2020-02-26}}</ref>\nOn 26 February 2020, the man's 24-year-old girlfriend and her 60-year-old father, a chief physician at University Hospital T\u00fcbingen, tested positive and were admitted to the same hospital.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.swp.de/suedwesten/staedte/reutlingen/coronavirus-tuebingen-zwei-bestaetigte-infektionen-mit-dem-corona-virus-am-uniklinikum-tuebingen-44066663.html|title=Coronavirus T\u00fcbingen: Zwei best\u00e4tigte Infektionen am Uniklinikum T\u00fcbingen|last=GmbH|first=S\u00fcdwest Presse Online-Dienste|date=2020-02-26|website=swp.de|language=de|access-date=2020-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.stuttgarter-zeitung.de/inhalt.coronavirus-in-tuebingen-ein-coronavirus-patient-ist-oberarzt-am-klinikum.1c316472-18b5-49b4-8759-2df4d433a245.html|title=Coronavirus in T\u00fcbingen: Ein Coronavirus-Patient ist Oberarzt am Klinikum|last=Germany|first=Stuttgarter Zeitung, Stuttgart|website=stuttgarter-zeitung.de|language=de|access-date=2020-02-26}}</ref> A 32-year-old man from [[Rottweil]], Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg who had visited Codogno with his family on 23 February tested positive and was admitted to a hospital for isolation.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sozialministerium.baden-wuerttemberg.de/de/service/presse/pressemitteilung/pid/neuer-bestaetigter-fall-von-corona-in-rottweil/|title=Neuer best\u00e4tigter Fall von Corona in Rottweil|website=Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg.de|language=de|access-date=2020-02-26}}</ref>\nOn 27 February, [[Bavaria]] confirmed that a man from [[Middle Franconia]] tested positive after having contact with an Italian man who later tested positive.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.web24.news/2020/02/bavaria-also-reports-another-new-corona-virus-case.html|title=Bavaria also reports another new corona virus case|last=admin|date=2020-02-27|website=Web24 News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref> Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg confirmed that two women and a man from [[Breisgau-Hochschwarzwald]] and [[Freiburg im Breisgau|Freiburg]], respectively, tested positive. They had contact with an Italian participant at a business meeting in [[Munich]] who tested positive in Italy. A man from [[B\u00f6blingen]] who had had contact with the girlfriend of the patient from G\u00f6ppingen also tested positive.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sozialministerium.baden-wuerttemberg.de/de/service/presse/pressemitteilung/pid/vier-weitere-bestaetigte-corona-faelle-in-baden-wuerttemberg/|title=Vier weitere best\u00e4tigte Corona-F\u00e4lle in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg|website=Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg.de|language=de|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref>\nOn 28 February, a man from [[Breisgau|Freiburg]] who had travelled to [[Bergamo]] tested positive and underwent isolation.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MSI_BW/status/1233390378147074049/photo/1|title=In Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg gibt es zwei weitere best\u00e4tigte Infektionen mit dem #Coronavirus (#Freiburg und #Karlsruhe). Damit sind es aktuell 12 F\u00e4lle im Land.pic.twitter.com/x71UZZMomN|last=BW|first=Ministerium f\u00fcr Soziales und Integration|date=2020-02-28|website=@MSI_BW|language=de|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref> A man from [[Rhine-Neckar]] was admitted to the [[University Hospital Heidelberg]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MSI_BW/status/1233333090896039936|title=In Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg gibt es seit dem sp\u00e4ten Donnerstagabend zwei neue best\u00e4tigte Corona-F\u00e4lle. Die Zahl steigt damit auf 10 F\u00e4lle im Land. #COVID2019pic.twitter.com/xBWAGlNOJC|last=BW|first=Ministerium f\u00fcr Soziales und Integration|date=2020-02-28|website=@MSI_BW|language=de|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref> A 32-year-old man in [[Heilbronn]] who was in Milan on 21 February fell ill and was admitted to a hospital.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MSI_BW/status/1233438797477621763/photo/1|title=In Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg wurde am Freitagnachmittag ein weiterer best\u00e4tigter #COVID2019 -Fall im Landkreis #Heilbronn bekannt. Damit steigt die Zahl in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg auf 13.pic.twitter.com/SnQ0UqctaX|last=BW|first=Ministerium f\u00fcr Soziales und Integration|date=2020-02-28|website=@MSI_BW|language=de|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref>\n\n[[File:Tbilisi TV Tower - March 23, Solidarity to Italy.jpg|thumb|On 23 March [[Tbilisi TV Broadcasting Tower|Tbilisi TV Tower]] was lit into the colours of the Italian flag to show Georgia's solidarity in the fight with the coronavirus.]]\n\n'''[[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]''' \u2013\nOn 28 February 2020, Georgia confirmed that a 31-year-old Georgian woman who had travelled to Italy tested positive and was admitted to Infectious Diseases Hospital in [[Tbilisi]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://agenda.ge/en/news/2020/620|title=Georgia reports second case of coronavirus|website=Agenda.ge|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Greece]]''' \u2013\nOn 26 February 2020, Greece confirmed its first case, a 38-year-old woman from [[Thessaloniki]] who had recently visited Northern Italy and was admitted to [[AHEPA University Hospital]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.naftemporiki.gr/story/1565985/covid-19-to-proto-thetiko-krousma-stin-ellada-38xroni|title=Covid-19: \u03a4\u03bf \u03c0\u03c1\u03ce\u03c4\u03bf \u03b8\u03b5\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03cc \u03ba\u03c1\u03bf\u03cd\u03c3\u03bc\u03b1 \u03c3\u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u0395\u03bb\u03bb\u03ac\u03b4\u03b1- 38\u03c7\u03c1\u03bf\u03bd\u03b7 \u03b1\u03c0\u03cc \u03c4\u03b7 \u0398\u03b5\u03c3\u03c3\u03b1\u03bb\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03ba\u03b7 |language=el |trans-title=Covid-19: The first positive case in Greece - 38 years old from Thessaloniki |date=26 February 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020 |publisher=www.naftemporiki.gr }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.gr/news/ellada/story/209034/o-koronaios-eftase-stin-ellada-proto-epivevaiomeno-kroysma-sti-thessaloniki|title=\u039f \u03ba\u03bf\u03c1\u03bf\